abstract: New York Giants Osi Umenyiora, defensive end, who is recovering from knee surgery, is listed as questionable in team's upcoming game against Arizona Cardinals.
snippet: Defensive end Osi Umenyiora is listed as questionable but says he feels fit enough to return for the Giants.
lead_paragraph: Defensive end Osi Umenyiora is listed as questionable but says he feels fit enough to return for the Giants.
